 *Recap Answers*

1. Making a website adapt to different screen sizes (PC, laptop, tablet & mobile)

2. Lets you apply CSS code only when a certain screen condition is true (i.e. a breakpoint)

3. Fixed             -> Uses set sizes, doesn't change with screen size
   Fluid             -> Uses flexible sizes
   Responsive layout -> Combines flexible size & media queries
   
