   Grid    -> Arrange items vertically & horizontally

   Flexbox would be used if you wanted an item in 1 column going down the page (i.e. a product, then below that another product, etc...)
   Grid would be used if you wanted those products to also sit next to each other
   i.e. a product, next to another, then down to 2 more products

